    excerpt: 'Digital wellbeing is about more than screen time limits. This guide introduces teenagers and families to practical mindfulness-based approaches to technology use, helping young people develop a more intentional, less reactive relationship with their devices.',
    metaDescription: 'Digital wellbeing and mindfulness guide for teenagers. Practical techniques for more intentional technology use, managing notification anxiety, building offline anchors, and developing a healthier relationship with devices.',
